---

<section>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">
        How It Works: <span class="text-rebel-green">The Complete System Approach</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        The Silverback Authority Method isn't about individual tactics—it's about building a complete lead generation system. Here's how we do it:
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-stretch">
      <!-- Left: Image -->
      <div class="flex items-stretch md:col-span-1">
        <img
          src="https://RebelApeCDN.b-cdn.net/featured-social-media-campaign.webp"
          alt="Social media marketing campaign"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Timeline Cards Stacked -->
      <div class="space-y-6 md:col-span-2">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-rebel-green rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-base">
                1
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Month 1: Foundation</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-snug">
                  We build the infrastructure first—conversion optimization, tracking setup, and technical foundation. Not the sexy part, but what makes everything work.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-rebel-green rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-base">
                2
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Month 2+: Ads Launch & Lead Generation</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-snug">
                  Google Ads go live, leads start flowing. The algorithm is learning, so we're gathering data and optimizing. We track everything: cost per lead, conversion rates, ad performance.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-rebel-green rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-base">
                3
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Months 3-6: Compounding Results</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-snug">
                  The algorithm learns, SEO kicks in, organic traffic grows, lead costs drop. The complete system shows its value—website + ads + SEO + tracking working together for predictable revenue.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-rebel-green rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-base">
                4
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Ongoing: Testing & Optimization</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-snug">
                  Marketing is testing. The company that tests the most wins. We continuously test ad copy, landing pages, and targeting to optimize performance. Active, daily optimization—not set-it-and-forget-it.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
